OL,7,FThe Education Committee has called on
OL,8,Fthe government to invest in programmes
OL,9,Fto boost recruitment, training and
OL,10,Fretention in a report published on
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,13,FRecruitment targets for initial
OL,14,Fteacher training courses were missed
OL,15,Fin 10 subjects in 2022/23, according
OL,16,Fto the committee, with maths, physics
OL,17,Fand religious education among the
OL,18,Fsubjects affected.
