OL,7,F"While there have been welcome
OL,8,Fincreases in absolute teacher numbers,
OL,9,Fthese have not kept pace with pupil
OL,10,Fnumbers, and there is broad agreement
OL,11,Ffrom witnesses that there is a crisis
OL,12,Fof teacher recruitment and retention
OL,13,Fin England," the report said.
OL,15,FIt added that there were "" about the
OL,16,Fnegative impacts of subject specific
OL,17,Fteacher shortages.
