OL,7,FEducation Committee chairman Robin
OL,8,FWalker said ministers need to rethink
OL,9,Fthe "recent, short-sighted that
OL,10,Fpromoted career development and
OL,11,Fdifferent routes into the profession".
OL,13,F"Without them we will keep on missing
OL,14,Ftargets for recruiting specialist
OL,15,Fteachers in nearly every subject,
OL,16,Fforcing more teachers to take on
OL,17,Fclasses outside of their specialism
OL,18,Fand thereby undermining the quality of
OL,19,Feducation children receive."
