OL,7,FAccording to the committee, many
OL,8,Fcurrent teachers singled out
OL,9,F"excessive workloads" rather than pay
OL,10,Fas the biggest factor pushing them to
OL,11,Fleave the sector.
OL,13,FIn the Department for Education's
OL,14,F(DfE) 2022 Working Lives of Teachers
OL,15,Fsurvey, 92% of participating teachers
OL,16,Fcited workload as a reason to quit the
OL,17,Fprofession, while 57% mentioned pay.
