OL,7,FTeachers were found to be dedicating
OL,8,Fmore time to offering students mental
OL,9,Fhealth support and family conflict
OL,10,Fresolution since the pandemic, with
OL,11,FEducation Support also saying teachers
OL,12,Fwere helping children to combat the
OL,13,Fcost-of-living crisis by buying meals
OL,14,Fand washing uniforms.
OL,16,F"We also heard that 'overspill' from
OL,17,Fwider social problems is heaping extra
OL,18,Fstress on teachers, be it children's
OL,19,Fmental health, behaviour, even cases
OL,20,Fof teachers helping families resolve
OL,21,Fdisputes," Mr Walker said.
