OL,7,FPupil behaviour has also worsened
OL,8,Fsince the pandemic, according to the
OL,9,Freport, which can "discourage" people
OL,10,Ffrom becoming teachers and make
OL,11,Fexisting teachers think about leaving
OL,12,Fthe profession.
OL,14,FIt was recommended that the government
OL,15,Fexpand its Behaviour Hubs programme,
OL,16,Fwhich helps school leaders to create
OL,17,Fpositive school environments, to allow
OL,18,Fmore schools to benefit from it.
