OL,7,FThe report also said teacher salaries
OL,8,F"need to be attractive" to boost
OL,9,Frecruitment and that while the
OL,10,Fintroduction of a #30,000 starting
OL,11,Fsalary was a welcome step, the figure
OL,12,Fwill have to increase in the coming
OL,13,Fyears "if it is to remain competitive".
OL,15,FThe Association of School and College
OL,16,FLeaders said the Education Committee
OL,17,Fidentified the problem "but not the
