OL,8,Fteachers now, record numbers of
OL,9,Fteachers in our schools, with over
OL,10,F468,000 in the workforce, a 27,000
OL,11,Fincrease since 2010, and 59,600 more
OL,12,Fteaching assistants since 2011.
OL,14,F"To continue attracting the best and
OL,15,Fbrightest, we offer bursaries and
OL,16,Fscholarships of up to #30,000 tax-free
OL,17,Fin the subject areas where they are
OL,18,Fneeded most, including physics and
OL,19,Fmaths, and opening new routes into the
OL,20,Fprofession, such as through teacher
OL,21,Fdegree apprenticeships.
